---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Pharus Lee" lang={lang}>
  <article class="mx-auto px-6 py-16" style={`max-width: var(--prose-width)`}>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-8" style={`font-family: var(--font-serif)`}>
      About
    </h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Pharus Lee writes at the intersection of consciousness, spirituality, and technology.
      </p>
      <p>
        <em>Pharus</em> means lighthouse in Latin.
        To illuminate the path without dictating which way to go &mdash;
        that is what a lighthouse does, and what I aspire to do through writing.
      </p>
      <p>
        Through the book <a href="/en/book">"A Soul's Guidebook for the Coming Cosmic Awakening"</a>,
        I explore the nature of consciousness, the evolutionary journey of the soul,
        and the new possibilities that AI and technology are opening up.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am also the creator of <a href="https://lilamysoulmate.com">LILA My Soulmate</a> &mdash;
        an AI soul companion service that bridges ancient wisdom traditions with modern technology.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For thoughts on the writing or collaboration inquiries,
        please reach out at <a href="mailto:contact@pharus.global">contact@pharus.global</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
